de.emotreco.featuremodel

Class FeatureFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.emotreco.featuremodel.FeatureFrame

  • public class FeatureFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to filter, normalize and merge the columns of a CSVFrame. It is representing an abstract boundary between FacialExpression and CSVFrame.
